S.FORM: laluma'an nu Matel i Tuen(Amilika a kamu: House Nymeros Martell of Sunspear , Hulan a kamu:陽戟城的馬泰爾家族 ) u cacay a laluma'an nu giki, dadiw nu sulda atu lamal(Amilika: A Song of Ice and Fire), u nisangaan nu misulitay ci George Raymond Richard Martin, u kungku nu nilalamelan nu laylay atu malawlaay nadatengan. izaw ku pituay a pu nu ulic nu nida. malagiki nu HBO i 2011 a mihcaan. laylay nu laluma'an nu Matel namakay i lekelikenan a bunga a sililinay a luma' ci Nameylos Matel, i nidebungan nu Antal a tedemaw tu Weystelo a lala' tayda i Tuen cinida, ci Mukan Matel ku mukeliday, muladay tu hitay nida micidakay atu lalangawan ayda a kasahenulay a tademaw tu laluma'an nu Matel Tulang Nameylos Matel Upelin Nameylos Matel Eylalia Sent malalitin tu ihekaay atu zumaay a natinengan nasulitan ni Padakaw Lami' 2020. u Wipsay nu misulitay ci Georgr RR Martin manamuhay a Wikipayke dadiw nu sulda atu lamal

laloma'an no Matel i Toen(Amilika a kamo: Hoose Nymeros Martell of Sonspear , Holan a kamo:陽戟城的馬泰爾家族 ) o cacay a laloma'an no giki, dadiw no solda ato lamal(Amilika: A Song of Ice and Fire), o nisangaan no misolitay ci George Raymond Richard Martin, o kongko no nilalamelan no laylay ato malawlaay nadatengan. izaw ko pitoay a po no olic no nida. malagiki no HBO i 2011 a mihcaan. laylay no laloma'an no Matel namakay i lekelikenan a bonga a sililinay a loma' ci Nameylos Matel, i nidebongan no Antal a tedemaw to Weystelo a lala' tayda i Toen cinida, ci Mokan Matel ko mokeliday, moladay to hitay nida micidakay ato lalangawan ayda a kasahenolay a tademaw to laloma'an no Matel Tolang Nameylos Matel Upelin Nameylos Matel Eylalia Sent malalitin to ihekaay ato zomaay a natinengan nasolitan ni Padakaw Lami' 2020. o Wipsay no misolitay ci Georgr RR Martin manamohay a Wikipayke dadiw no solda ato lamal
